<subSubSection id="AC92657BFFA0FFC4FF23F8EEFD473ACE" pageId="0" pageNumber="115" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph id="E43736F0FFA0FFC4FF23F8EEFA3A3A29" blockId="0.[136,1452,1386,1950]" box="[189,1451,1890,1914]" pageId="0" pageNumber="115">
<emphasis id="D6FCEAE2FFA0FFC4FF23F8EEFEAB3A2A" bold="true" box="[189,314,1890,1914]" pageId="0" pageNumber="115">Ecology:—</emphasis>
The species grows in mossy place on limestone cliff along a valley, at an elevation between 900 and 
<specimenCount id="F28EFD79FFA0FFC4FAFFF8EEFA3A3A29" box="[1377,1451,1890,1914]" pageId="0" pageNumber="115" type="generic">
<quantity id="23709B15FFA0FFC4FAFFF8EEFA363A29" box="[1377,1447,1890,1914]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.1" pageId="0" pageNumber="115" unit="m" value="910.0">910 m</quantity>
.
</specimenCount>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E43736F0FFA0FFC4FF23F80AFD473ACE" blockId="0.[136,1452,1386,1950]" box="[189,726,1926,1950]" pageId="0" pageNumber="115">
<emphasis id="D6FCEAE2FFA0FFC4FF23F80AFEC93ACE" bold="true" box="[189,344,1926,1950]" pageId="0" pageNumber="115">Phenology:—</emphasis>
Flowering period from June to July.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
