<subSubSection id="AC92657BFFA2FFC6FF23F8CDFCB83A95" pageId="2" pageNumber="117" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="E43736F0FFA2FFC6FF23F8CDFCB83A95" blockId="2.[136,1452,1857,1989]" pageId="2" pageNumber="117">
<emphasis id="D6FCEAE2FFA2FFC6FF23F8CDFE683A09" bold="true" box="[189,505,1857,1881]" pageId="2" pageNumber="117">Taxonomic relationships:—</emphasis>
This new species is similar to 
<taxonomicName id="23884D73FFA2FFC6FCD2F8CDFBF33A09" box="[844,1122,1857,1881]" class="Liliopsida" family="Orchidaceae" genus="Amitostigma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="2" pageNumber="117" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pinguiculum">
<emphasis id="D6FCEAE2FFA2FFC6FCD2F8CDFBF33A09" box="[844,1122,1857,1881]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="117">Amitostigma pinguiculum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, from which it differs mainly by its distribution, flowering period and morphological characteristics, such as much broader leaf to 
<quantity id="23709B15FFA2FFC6FB52F8E9FAD43A2D" box="[1228,1349,1893,1917]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.3" metricValueMax="3.8" metricValueMin="2.8" pageId="2" pageNumber="117" unit="cm" value="3.3" valueMax="3.8" valueMin="2.8">2.8–3.8 cm</quantity>
wide, lip trilobed near middle, lobes with irregularly denticulate-margined apically, side-lobes obovate-oblong and mid-lobe oblong. Detailed comparison of the two species is presented in 
<tableCitation id="A90A034BFFA2FFC6FD4DF821FCB33A95" box="[723,802,1965,1989]" captionStart="TABLE 1" captionStartId="3.[136,224,159,183]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="TABLE 1. A comparison of Amitostigma kaiyangense and A. pinguiculum." httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/B0F76678FFA3FFC7FF16FF13FC3E3DE7" pageId="2" pageNumber="117" tableUuid="B0F76678FFA3FFC7FF16FF13FC3E3DE7">Table 1</tableCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<caption id="B0F76678FFA3FFC7FF16FF13FC3E3DE7" ID-Table-UUID="B0F76678FFA3FFC7FF16FF13FC3E3DE7" box="[136,943,159,183]" httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/B0F76678FFA3FFC7FF16FF13FC3E3DE7" pageId="3" pageNumber="118" startId="3.[136,224,159,183]" targetBox="[144,1439,209,760]" targetIsTable="true" targetPageId="3">
